From f31d486cafe4f8a3bdc1134b9ef48d8ea4194860 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: LordAfterEight <elias@stettmayer.de>
Date: Thu, 16 Jul 2026 20:22:23 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] hw/display: add STM32H7 LTDC layer-1 scanout

Model enough LTDC registers for ArmOS (timings, layer1 ARGB8888,
CFBAR/reload, GCR enable) and present the guest framebuffer in a
QEMU graphic console (~30 Hz). Wire LTDC into stm32h745-soc.
---
